    "created_at": "2013-12-30T00:19:12Z",
    "updated_at": "2013-12-30T00:19:12Z",
    "body": "How about adding blocking receive with a timeout to channels and using `sleep(reltime)` and `sleep_until(abstime)` in other cases? It would be unnecessary to use a select abstraction if channels had the functionality built-in, and it's a natural operation to perform on a condition variable.\n",
