    "created_at": "2013-12-30T00:25:47Z",
    "updated_at": "2013-12-30T00:25:47Z",
    "body": "I agree that if channels had timeout functionality built in that much of this might not be necessary, but I personally do not know how to do this efficiently.\n\nFor now though, this should probably be discussed in a separate issue. I would still like to have an API with timers as channels, and if we can later upgrade the implementation to use receive with timeouts that's great, but we don't have the ability to do that right now.\n",
